KernelPatch / KPM
-----------------

The KPM compatibility bridge is derived from SukiSU-Ultra and uses the
SukiSU KernelPatch patch set:

  https://github.com/SukiSU-Ultra/SukiSU-Ultra
  https://github.com/SukiSU-Ultra/SukiSU_KernelPatch_patch

The bundled kpimg and Android kptools binaries are the matching 0.13.0
release artifacts. Their source is licensed under GPL-2.0-or-later.
The artifacts are pinned and verified at runtime with SHA-256.
